narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Take if you're making a doc for your senior project.

If you need to take this class for your senior project, then do it. You have to be extremely self-motivated because nothing happens in the class. Make sure that you have taken intro because this class won't actually teach you anything.
Perfect arena for critique on a work in progress senior project, otherwise not the course for you.

take this class if you want to make a extensive documentary, best to have a project in the works that you have begun over the summer or start quickly. But can be done by anyone who has the aspiration of making a documentary project
